# NOTE: expo-env.d.ts is committed on purpose — tsconfig `include`s it and it provides
# the `*.css` (and asset) module declarations via `expo/types`. Without it CI `tsc`
# fails on `import "@/global.css"` (TS2882). Expo regenerates it with identical content.

